KnownSerialFlashes:
Atmel AT25DF161 tested by customer
Atmel AT26DF161A
Atmel AT26DF161
Atmel AT26DF321
Atmel AT45DB081D
Atmel AT45DB161D
Atmel AT45DB321C this must be before the ATDB321B typ, or this will never match
Atmel AT45DB321D this must be before the ATDB321B typ, or this will never match
Atmel AT45DB642D
NexFlash NX25P10
NexFlash NX25P20
NexFlash NX25P40
SST SST25LF20A or SST25VF020
SST SST25LF40A or SST25VF040
SST SST25LF80A
SST SST25VF010 or SST25VF010A
SST SST25VF512 or SST25VF512A
PMC PM25LV512
PMC PM25LV010
Saifun SA25F005
ST M25P10VP (tested), Numonyx M25P10-A This entry must precede the Saifun SA25F010 entry to avoid confusion.
Saifun SA25F020 the obsolete ST M25P20 will also match, it is not recommended (has no page erase)
M25P40 this is compatible to the Saifun SA25F040. The only difference is the clock speed. The SA25F040 supports up to 50MHz, but the M25P40 'only' runs at 25MHz.
ST M45PE20
ST M45PE40
ST M45PE80
